snippet.title: Idle Tap Airport - Gameplay Walkthrough Part 1 (IOS, Android)
snippet.description:
The airport is under your control. Upgrade your check-in to move passengers through your airport quicker. The more passengers the bigger your airport will become. Fasten your seatbelts, it's take-off time.

Google play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.neonplay.casualidletapairport

Apple store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/idle-tap-airport/id1482904441
